  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.1">
<l>ēḻai yōtalaṉ kīḻmaka ṉeṉṉā tiraṅki maṟṟavaṟ kiṉṉaruḷ curantu</l>
<l>māḻai māṉmaṭa nōkkiyuṉ tōḻi yumpi yempiyeṉ ṟoḻintilai yukantu</l>
<l>tōḻa ṉīyeṉak kiṅkoḻi yeṉṟa coṟkaḷ vantaṭi yēṉmaṉat tiruntiṭa</l>
<l>vāḻi vaṇṇaniṉ ṉaṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkattam  māṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without calling [him] a simple, poor, and low man,</l>
<l rend="indent">[but] showing compassion, lavishing sweet grace on that other,</l>
<l>Saying, “She with the simple glance of a young deer is your friend;</l>
<l rend="indent">My younger brother is your younger brother,”</l>
<l>And, rejoicing, you who did not forsake  [him] said, “And you are my friend;</l>
<l rend="indent">stay here”; as [these] words, coming into my mind, remain firmly,</l>
<l>Sea-hued [lord], I took refuge at your two feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
